<seg id=1> Dinosaur Bone Fossil Found in Henan Xixia </seg>
</hl>
<p>
<seg id=2> Xinhua News Agency, Zhengzhou, April 23 (by Journalist Liu Yamin) - Recently, some interested specialists and scholars have found plenty of dinosaur bone fossil in Yancheng town, Xixia county of Henan province. </seg>
<seg id=3> This was another significant discovery followed the findings of rich precious dinosaur egg fossils in this same place last year. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=4> The journalist knew from the Cultural Relic Archaeology Research Institute of Henan Province, at the beginning of April this year, the relevant specialists found several hundred pieces of dinosaur bone fossils, some were rib and phalange etc, between two river gravel layers in places of Hutoushan mountain, Yancheng town of Xixia county. </seg>
<seg id=5> Because of their long time exposure on the ground surface, some of them were broken. </seg>
<seg id=6> From the stratigraphy point of view, all of them belong to the Cretaceous Period. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=7> According to specialist's judgment, there could be a great number of dinosaur bone fossils and fossils of other species in this dinosaur fossil concentrated area. </seg>
<seg id=8> They thought, if the finding of plenty precious dinosaur egg fossils in Xixia basin is a rare case in the world, the discovery of both egg fossils and bone fossils in the same place will be much more scarce. </seg>
<seg id=9> This has a very important significance for studies of classification of dinosaur in Xixia area, probe of the dinosaur ecological habit and propagation behavior, restoration of ecological environment of dinosaur times, revelation of the rules of the earth's crust transition and earth environment evolution etc. </seg>
<seg id=10> And the finding of dinosaur bone fossils will provide important clues for searching the geographical location and burying rules of the dinosaur fossils. </seg>
</p>
